{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":214,"text":"There's currently over a thousand\nTED Talks on the TED website."},{"time":4394,"text":"And I guess many of you here\nthink that this is quite fantastic,"},{"time":9414,"text":"except for me, I don't agree with this."},{"time":11312,"text":"I think we have a situation here."},{"time":12921,"text":"Because if you think about it,\n1,000 TED Talks,"},{"time":16396,"text":"that's over 1,000 ideas worth spreading."},{"time":19853,"text":"How on earth are you going\nto spread a thousand ideas?"},{"time":23466,"text":"Even if you just try\nto get all of those ideas into your head"},{"time":26358,"text":"by watching all those thousand TED videos,"},{"time":28403,"text":"it would actually currently take you\nover 250 hours to do so."},{"time":32563,"text":"And I did a little calculation of this."},{"time":35151,"text":"The damage to the economy for each one\nwho does this is around $15,000."},{"time":39680,"text":"So having seen this danger to the economy,"},{"time":43237,"text":"I thought, we need to find\na solution to this problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46364,"text":"Here's my approach to it all."},{"time":48146,"text":"If you look at the current situation,\nyou have a thousand TED Talks."},{"time":51376,"text":"Each of those TED Talks has\nan average length of about 2,300 words."},{"time":56275,"text":"Now take this together, and you end up\nwith 2.3 million words of TED Talks,"},{"time":60999,"text":"which is about\nthree Bibles-worth of content."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63709,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64734,"text":"The obvious question here is,\ndoes a TED Talk really need 2,300 words?"},{"time":69214,"text":"Isn't there something shorter?"},{"time":70703,"text":"I mean, if you have\nan idea worth spreading,"},{"time":72807,"text":"surely you can put it\ninto something shorter than 2,300 words."},{"time":76289,"text":"The only question is,\nhow short can you get?"},{"time":79007,"text":"What's the minimum amount of words\nyou would need to do a TED Talk?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82945,"text":"While I was pondering this question,"},{"time":84691,"text":"I came across this urban legend\nabout Ernest Hemingway,"},{"time":87912,"text":"who allegedly said\nthat these six words here:"},{"time":91008,"text":"\"For sale: baby shoes, never worn,\""},{"time":93884,"text":"were the best novel he had ever written."},{"time":96622,"text":"And I also encountered a project\ncalled Six-Word Memoirs"},{"time":99272,"text":"where people were asked,\ntake your whole life"},{"time":101416,"text":"and please sum this up\ninto six words, such as these here:"},{"time":104176,"text":"\"Found true love, married someone else.\""},{"time":106211,"text":"Or \"Living in existential\nvacuum; it sucks.\""},{"time":108610,"text":"I actually like that one."},{"time":110692,"text":"So if a novel can be put into six words"},{"time":113112,"text":"and a whole memoir can be put\ninto six words,"},{"time":116718,"text":"you don't need more than six\nwords for a TED Talk."},{"time":119663,"text":"We could have been done by lunch here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122905,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":124412,"text":"And if you did this\nfor all thousand TED Talks,"},{"time":126646,"text":"you would get from 2.3 million\nwords down to 6,000."},{"time":129998,"text":"So I thought this was quite worthwhile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131895,"text":"So I started asking all my friends,"},{"time":133677,"text":"please take your favorite TED Talk\nand put that into six words."},{"time":136699,"text":"So here are some of the results\nthat I received."},{"time":138967,"text":"I think they're quite nice."},{"time":140339,"text":"For example, Dan Pink's talk\non motivation, which was pretty good,"},{"time":143463,"text":"if you haven't seen it:\n\"Drop carrot. Drop stick. Bring meaning.\""},{"time":146593,"text":"It's what he's basically talking about\nin those 18,5 minutes."},{"time":149489,"text":"Or some even included references\nto the speakers,"},{"time":151807,"text":"such as Nathan Myhrvold's speaking style,\nor the one of Tim Ferriss,"},{"time":155035,"text":"which might be considered\na bit strenuous at times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157468,"text":"The challenge here is,\nif I try to systematically do this,"},{"time":160213,"text":"I would probably end up\nwith a lot of summaries,"},{"time":162562,"text":"but not with many friends in the end."},{"time":164358,"text":"So I had to find a different method,\npreferably involving total strangers."},{"time":167877,"text":"And luckily, there's a website for that,\ncalled Mechanical Turk,"},{"time":171237,"text":"which is a website\nwhere you can post tasks"},{"time":173429,"text":"that you don't want to do yourself,"},{"time":175143,"text":"such as \"Please summarize this text\nfor me in six words.\""},{"time":178172,"text":"And I didn't allow any low-cost\ncountries to work on this,"},{"time":181031,"text":"but I found out I could get\na six-word summary for just 10 cents,"},{"time":184755,"text":"which I think is a pretty good price."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187025,"text":"Even then, unfortunately,"},{"time":188749,"text":"it's not possible to summarize\neach TED Talk individually."},{"time":191618,"text":"Because if you do the math,\nyou have a thousand TED Talks,"},{"time":194396,"text":"you pay 10 cents each;"},{"time":195586,"text":"you have to do more than one summary\nfor each of those talks,"},{"time":198555,"text":"because some of them will probably\nbe, or are, really bad."},{"time":201366,"text":"So I would end up paying\nhundreds of dollars."},{"time":204200,"text":"So I thought of a different way,"},{"time":206000,"text":"by thinking, well, the talks\nrevolve around certain themes."},{"time":209398,"text":"So what if I don't let people summarize\nindividual TED Talks to six words,"},{"time":214083,"text":"but give them 10 TED Talks\nat the same time"},{"time":216123,"text":"and say, \"Please do a six-word\nsummary for that one.\""},{"time":218768,"text":"I would cut my costs by 90 percent."},{"time":220955,"text":"So for $60,"},{"time":223509,"text":"I could summarize a thousand TED Talks\ninto just 600 summaries,"},{"time":227524,"text":"which would actually be quite nice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229546,"text":"Some of you might actually\nright now be thinking,"},{"time":231863,"text":"it's downright crazy to have 10 TED Talks\nsummarized into just six words."},{"time":235385,"text":"But it's actually not,"},{"time":236689,"text":"because there's an example\nby statistics professor Hans Rosling."},{"time":239842,"text":"I guess many of you have seen\none or more of his talks."},{"time":242452,"text":"He's got eight talks online,"},{"time":243812,"text":"and those can basically be summed up\ninto just four words,"},{"time":246552,"text":"because that's all he's basically\nshowing us, our intuition is really bad."},{"time":251180,"text":"He always proves us wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252570,"text":"So people on the Internet,\nsome didn't do so well."},{"time":255157,"text":"And when I asked them to summarize\nthe 10 TED Talks at the same time,"},{"time":258574,"text":"some took the easy route out."},{"time":260078,"text":"They just had some general comment."},{"time":262513,"text":"There were others --\nand I found this quite cheeky --"},{"time":265573,"text":"They used their six words\nto talk back to me"},{"time":268007,"text":"and ask me if I'd been too much\non Google lately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270340,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":271523,"text":"And finally also, I never understood this,"},{"time":274640,"text":"some people really came up\nwith their own version of the truth."},{"time":277798,"text":"I don't know any TED Talk\nthat contains this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280631,"text":"But, oh well."},{"time":282205,"text":"In the end, however,\nand this is really amazing,"},{"time":284565,"text":"for each of those 10 TED Talk\nclusters that I submitted,"},{"time":287429,"text":"I actually received meaningful summaries."},{"time":289415,"text":"Here are some of my favorites."},{"time":290882,"text":"For example, for the TED Talks about food,"},{"time":293186,"text":"someone summed this up into: \"Food shaping\nbody, brains and environment,\""},{"time":296669,"text":"which I think is pretty good."},{"time":298081,"text":"Or happiness: \"Striving toward happiness =\nmoving toward unhappiness.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":301395,"text":"So here I was."},{"time":302572,"text":"I had started out\nwith a thousand TED Talks"},{"time":304606,"text":"and I had 600 six-word\nsummaries for those."},{"time":308030,"text":"Actually, it sounded nice\nin the beginning,"},{"time":310057,"text":"but when you look at 600 summaries,\nit's quite a lot, it's a huge list."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313479,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":314518,"text":"So I thought, I probably have\nto take this one step further here"},{"time":317600,"text":"and create summaries of the summaries,\nand this is exactly what I did."},{"time":321252,"text":"So I took the 600 summaries that I had,\nput them into nine groups"},{"time":324546,"text":"according to the ratings that the talks\nhad originally received on TED.com"},{"time":328458,"text":"and asked people to do summaries of those."},{"time":331779,"text":"Again, there were some misunderstandings."},{"time":333775,"text":"For example, when I had a cluster\nof all the \"Beautiful\" talks,"},{"time":336764,"text":"someone thought I was just trying\nto find the ultimate pick-up line."},{"time":340007,"text":"But in the end, amazingly,"},{"time":342208,"text":"again, people were able to do it."},{"time":343813,"text":"For example, all the courageous TED Talks:"},{"time":345891,"text":"\"People dying\" or \"People\nsuffering\" was also one,"},{"time":348354,"text":"\"with easy solutions around.\""},{"time":349775,"text":"Or the recipe for the ultimate\njaw-dropping TED Talk:"},{"time":352284,"text":"\"Flickr photos of intergalactic\nclassical composer.\""},{"time":354839,"text":"I mean that's the essence of it all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357712,"text":"Now I had my nine groups, but, I mean,\nit's already quite a reduction."},{"time":362708,"text":"But of course, once you are that far,\nyou're not really satisfied."},{"time":366167,"text":"I wanted to go all the way,\nall the way down the distillery,"},{"time":369016,"text":"starting out with a thousand TED Talks."},{"time":370930,"text":"I wanted to have a thousand TED Talks\nsummarized into just six words --"},{"time":374318,"text":"which would be a 99.9997 percent\nreduction in content."},{"time":377820,"text":"And I would only pay $99.50 --"},{"time":381481,"text":"so stay even below $100 for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384610,"text":"So I had 50 overall summaries done."},{"time":386327,"text":"This time I paid 25 cents"},{"time":387759,"text":"because I thought the task\nwas a bit harder."},{"time":389887,"text":"And unfortunately,\nwhen I first received the answers --"},{"time":393339,"text":"and here, you'll see six of the answers --\nI was a bit disappointed."},{"time":396581,"text":"Because I think you'll agree,\nthey all summarize some aspect of TED,"},{"time":399829,"text":"but to me, they felt a bit bland,"},{"time":401777,"text":"or they just had\na certain aspect of TED in them."},{"time":405070,"text":"So I was almost ready to give up"},{"time":406858,"text":"when one night, I played around\nwith these sentences"},{"time":409981,"text":"and found out that there's actually\na beautiful solution in here."},{"time":413928,"text":"So here it is,"},{"time":416316,"text":"a crowd-sourced, six-word\nsummary of a thousand TED Talks"},{"time":420322,"text":"at the value of $99.50:"},{"time":423530,"text":"\"Why the worry? I'd rather wonder.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":426196,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427483,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}